#ROOMS
#300
@@GThe Preparation Room@@N~
You are standing in a small square room with rough stone walls. The walls are
lined with sturdy oak @@Gbenches@@N, and those benches are crowded with gladiators
waiting for their turn to fight to the death in the arena. The air is thick
with sweat and nervous energy. To the east, a narrow passage leads deeper into
the arena grounds. A heavy iron gate to the west opens onto the road beyond.
~
