#301
@@GTraining Camp@@N~
Weapon racks and scarred practice dummies crowd this dusty training yard. Boot
prints churn the packed earth in every direction, and the bark of drill
sergeants echoes off the surrounding arena walls. Battered wooden posts bear
the marks of countless strikes, their surfaces splintered and gouged.
