#304
@@GCombat Ground@@N~
This is the arena's combat ground, a broad pit of trampled sand stained dark
with old blood. Crude wooden barriers ring the fighting pit while spectators
roar from weathered stands beyond. The sand crunches underfoot, hiding
fragments of broken weapons and shattered shields. A heavy gate to the west
leads back toward the training lanes. The eastern passage opens toward the mess
hall where survivors take their meals.
~
