#305
@@GMess Hall@@N~
Long tables fill the mess hall, crowded with dented cups and chipped wooden
bowls. The smell of broth, sweat, and smoke hangs heavy in the warm air.
Fighters crowd the benches shoulder to shoulder, eating quickly with one eye
always watching the door.
