@@GKitchen@@N~
Heat rolls from brick ovens and blackened cookfires in this cramped kitchen.
Knives clatter on worn butcher blocks while cauldrons of stew simmer over open
flame. Soot coats the low ceiling and grease spatters mark the stone walls on
every side.
