@@GIn a Cell@@N~
Cold stone walls and rusted iron bars make this cell feel smaller by the
minute. Straw is scattered across the damp floor, and distant screams seep in
from the arena outside. Scratched tally marks cover the wall near a thin
sleeping pallet in the corner.
