@@GSupply Room@@N~
Shelves of clay pots, dried herbs, and sacks of grain line the walls of this
cramped supply room. Barrels of salted meat and casks of cheap ale are stacked
haphazardly in the corners. The air smells of dust, dried thyme, and old wood
that has seen better days.
